----------------NEEDED LIBRARIES AND INSTALLATION :


----------------FUZZYLITE :

https://github.com/fuzzylite/fuzzylite

DOWNLOAD SOURCE FROM GITHUB

cmake . && make && make install

----------------LEMON :

http://lemon.cs.elte.hu/

DOWNLOAD

cd lemon-x.y.z
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. && make && make install


----------------QHTTPSERVER :

https://github.com/nikhilm/qhttpserver

Requires Qt 4 or Qt 5.

qmake && make && su -c 'make install'

To link to your projects put this in your project's qmake project file

LIBS += -lqhttpserver

By default, the installation prefix is /usr/local. To change that to /usr,
for example, run:

qmake -r PREFIX=/usr